# Claude4Free Project Overview

## Project Description
Claude4Free is a multi-functional AI assistant web application that provides free access to various AI models including Claude, GPT-4, Gemini, and others. The application supports chat, image recognition, text-to-speech, and text-to-image generation.

## Architecture
This is a **serverless web application** built with:
- **Frontend**: AMP (Accelerated Mobile Pages) static website
- **Backend**: Cloudflare Workers API
- **Deployment**: Cloudflare Pages (frontend) + Cloudflare Workers (backend)

## Key Files
- [index.html](mdc:index.html) - Main AMP webpage (root level, legacy)
- [frontend/index.html](mdc:frontend/index.html) - Production frontend code
- [backend/api-server.js](mdc:backend/api-server.js) - Cloudflare Workers API handler
